{
  "stem": "1873.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was the driver of a little railroad, a small railroad, which connected two parts of the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I called him to try a leather coat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the same thing happened to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember, I went to this-- to this little railroad, like the mines have such-- coal mines have this little railroad.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I looked inside, and there were foodstuffs, canned foodstuff, canned foodstuff, fish and so on, sardines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I put  it in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember, I had a friend, his name was [POLISH] Karolek, Blind Karl.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Blind Karl looks at me and said, you're packing like for a picnic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're sure you will survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I told him, if I survive, I will use it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If not, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How heavy is it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used it, later, though, and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, in the matter of one hour, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Cohen ?] had come from another part of the camp, where the-- where the craftsmen were working, and told us that the deputy commandant was killed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, by 5 o'clock, most of them were killed, of the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quiet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At 5 o'clock, as usual, a prisoner went to the tower and put a signal out, with a trumpet, to end the work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The kapos assembled it, like every day, because the rule was, it should look like every day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the two kapos, which were  in the organization, were ordered even to beat us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's every day, if somebody is slow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we assembled in groups, and we marched to the kitchen, to the main yard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And now, I remember, when I marched in, I was shocked to see how many people don't know what's happened.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
